faq.answer:
Select will close when it lose focus. You can prevent event to handle this:

```tsx
<Select
  dropdownRender={() => (
    <div
      onMouseDown={(e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
      }}
    >
      Some Content
    </div>
  )}
/>
```

